videos.description: Florida's Kevarrius Hayes gets the block and then Chris Chiozza finds Hayes with the nice bounce pass for the layup.
videos.headline: Defense leads to offense for Florida

videos.description: J.J Frazier makes the 3-pointer over the taller defender to cap a 15-0 run for Georgia.
videos.headline: Georgia answer back with a 15-0 run

videos.description: Florida's Kevarrius Hayes comes out of nowhere and gets the big block.
videos.headline: Florida's Hayes with the huge block

videos.description: Florida gets the steal and goes out running, Keith Stone finds Canyon Barry who drains the wide-open 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Florida's Barry drains wide-open 3-pointer

videos.description: Chris Chiozza uses the pick and drains the deep 3-pointer for Florida.
videos.headline: Florida's Chiozza leaves his mark with deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Florida's Chris Chiozza breaks down the Gators' 72-60 victory over Georgia.
videos.headline: Chiozza shines on defense

videos.description: Chris Chiozza leads No. 17 Florida with 15 points off the bench in a 72-60 win over Georgia.
videos.headline: Chiozza strong for Florida off bench in win
